


// To create one style menu for elementor, first of all, you need to buy Elementor Pro. You need that, because to use Custom CSS, you can only do by using Elementor Pro.
// To create a fixed header section, you need to select a header section settings and click on advanced tab. Go to Custom CSS and copy this code below. Please after 
that you need to be sure if the section was mark down as stretched section on layout tab. 

selector { position: fixed
: top: 0}

// To create a fixed bottom section, you will do the same as above, but the code was a little bit different. Copy and paste this code below to create
//a fixed bottom section

selector { position: fixed;bottom: 0;}
